580
00:44:09,230 --> 00:44:12,070
Sung-woo, Oh Min-u, and Ho-yeol
will chase you and Ms. Shin.

581
00:44:13,320 --> 00:44:15,570
You and Hye-yeon
need to create a distraction.

582
00:44:16,950 --> 00:44:20,410
-Sir, what do you mean…
-Just listen, you punk. It's okay.

583
00:44:21,410 --> 00:44:22,410
Trust me.

584
00:44:24,380 --> 00:44:25,380
Jun-ho…

585
00:44:26,130 --> 00:44:27,670
The USB, where is it?

586
00:44:29,550 --> 00:44:30,380
Hang on.

587
00:44:30,960 --> 00:44:33,050
This was all a distraction to buy time?

588
00:44:34,800 --> 00:44:36,890
Hey, dumbass, don't you see?

589
00:44:38,390 --> 00:44:40,310
Beom-gu tricked the both of us.

590
00:44:45,190 --> 00:44:47,650
Did you think exposing them
would be that easy?

591
00:44:53,280 --> 00:44:55,820
I will now announce
the verdict taking into account

592
00:44:55,910 --> 00:44:57,280
the plaintiff's evidence.

593
00:44:58,660 --> 00:45:00,830
The judicial assessment and verdict

594
00:45:00,910 --> 00:45:04,080
concerning the compensation due
in this lawsuit,

595
00:45:05,420 --> 00:45:09,210
that was filed by the plaintiff,
the military victims and related persons,

596
00:45:09,290 --> 00:45:11,420
against the defendant, the State,

597
00:45:12,460 --> 00:45:13,800
is as follows.

598
00:45:16,930 --> 00:45:17,930
Verdict.

599
00:45:18,760 --> 00:45:21,100
The court accepts the plaintiff's claim

600
00:45:21,180 --> 00:45:24,850
