the State, which includes the military.

601
00:45:24,940 --> 00:45:28,020
It also includes commanders,
prosecutors, and investigators.

602
00:45:39,030 --> 00:45:40,280
However…

603
00:45:40,370 --> 00:45:42,910
the acknowledgement includes some cases.

604
00:45:43,410 --> 00:45:44,870
As for the other cases,

605
00:45:45,370 --> 00:45:47,880
it was decided
that some evidence is needed.

606
00:45:47,960 --> 00:45:50,920
Therefore, the ruling would be delayed.

607
00:46:00,890 --> 00:46:02,600
The court is now adjourned.

608
00:46:24,790 --> 00:46:26,210
Don't… Don't worry.

609
00:46:30,040 --> 00:46:31,630
I'm… I'm sorry.

610
00:46:32,170 --> 00:46:33,590
I'm… I'm sorry.

611
00:46:35,840 --> 00:46:39,220
I'm sorry. I'm…
I'm sorry for all I've done.

612
00:46:41,890 --> 00:46:43,600
Mom, don't worry.

613
00:46:43,680 --> 00:46:45,890
Mom, don't worry.

614
00:46:46,680 --> 00:46:48,100
Take care of yourself.

615
00:46:48,600 --> 00:46:50,310
Mom, don't worry!

616
00:46:58,610 --> 00:46:59,610
It's over.

617
00:47:08,830 --> 00:47:09,830
Great work.

618
00:47:11,460 --> 00:47:12,630
You too.

619
00:47:20,550 --> 00:47:22,260
I guess this counts as a tie?

620
00:47:26,770 --> 00:47:28,600
You know there will be consequences.

621
00:47:43,450 --> 00:47:44,410
Shit.

622
00:47:45,240 --> 00:47:46,080
Sir.

623
00:47:51,210 --> 00:47:52,920
Sergeant First Class Park,

624
00:47:53,000 --> 00:47:56,250
you are charged with leaking
classified information and violating…

625
00:48:38,750 --> 00:48:40,670
Oh, no. Sergeant Park.

626
00:48:49,430 --> 00:48:51,140
Let's have a smoke, then we'll go.

627
00:49:00,230 --> 00:49:01,230
Why would you…

628
00:49:03,900 --> 00:49:04,740
Why…

629
00:49:08,410 --> 00:49:10,410
Why… Why did you do that, Sergeant Park?

630
00:49:11,540 --> 00:49:13,250
I'm the one who started this.

631
00:49:15,080 --> 00:49:19,040
Think about what you've done.
You didn't see this coming?

632
00:49:29,010 --> 00:49:30,180
Hey, D.P.'s.

633
00:49:34,180 --> 00:49:35,020
Hey, D.P.'s!

634
00:49:35,980 --> 00:49:37,770
Yes… Yes, sir.

635
00:49:41,440 --> 00:49:43,570
Enjoy life when you're on the outside.

636
00:49:45,530 --> 00:49:47,780
And don't slack off too much, you punk.

637
00:49:49,160 --> 00:49:50,330
Okay.

638
00:49:54,450 --> 00:49:58,500
After your stint in jail, continue to
work hard and serve with integrity

639
00:49:58,580 --> 00:49:59,540
until the end.

640
00:50:02,210 --> 00:50:03,880
Even if it's a shithole.

641
00:50:05,260 --> 00:50:06,510
Understood?

642
00:50:07,720 --> 00:50:09,180
Mm… Yes.

643
00:50:21,860 --> 00:50:22,900
It's okay.

644
00:50:25,490 --> 00:50:27,320
It's okay, boys.

645
00:50:36,710 --> 00:50:37,960
Oh, shit.

646
00:50:40,540 --> 00:50:41,540
Let's go.

647
00:51:03,150 --> 00:51:07,860
CORRECTIONS

648
00:51:17,870 --> 00:51:19,120
Is this a joke?

649
00:51:22,460 --> 00:51:25,550
See, didn't I say that this would be
taking things a bit too far?

650
00:51:27,130 --> 00:51:29,220
You were so creative
getting yourself into prison,

651
00:51:29,300 --> 00:51:30,970
I thought you'd like to eat creative too.

652
00:51:31,050 --> 00:51:32,430
You bastard, I swear…

653
00:51:32,510 --> 00:51:34,140
No problem, I'll eat it.

654
00:51:36,720 --> 00:51:37,720
Give it here.

655
00:51:43,110 --> 00:51:44,060
Well done.

656
00:51:44,150 --> 00:51:46,980
But, sir, will this be worth it?

657
00:51:48,030 --> 00:51:50,030
You're locked up in here, sir,

658
00:51:51,400 --> 00:51:52,570
and we didn't even win--

659
00:51:52,660 --> 00:51:53,910
Did we lose, then?

660
00:51:59,250 --> 00:52:00,830
Next time, we'll win.

661
00:52:09,210 --> 00:52:10,590
Stop saying dumb crap,

662
00:52:10,670 --> 00:52:13,510
and go get me some cigarettes
at the commissary.

663
00:52:14,010 --> 00:52:15,890
But smoking's not allowed.

664
00:52:17,720 --> 00:52:19,600
And I'm taking this opportunity
to sneak one.

665
00:52:19,680 --> 00:52:20,680
All right.

666
00:52:21,350 --> 00:52:22,230
Come on.

667
00:52:24,020 --> 00:52:24,940
Let's go.

668
00:52:45,330 --> 00:52:47,340
I wonder why you didn't let me join you?

669
00:52:49,300 --> 00:52:50,210
Hmm?

670
00:52:51,170 --> 00:52:52,590
You've taken all the blame.

671
00:52:53,880 --> 00:52:56,300
Well, if someone has to lose his job,

672
00:52:56,390 --> 00:52:58,350
it's better it's a lowly sergeant
than the captain.

673
00:52:59,140 --> 00:53:00,930
Not everyone gets to be the hero.

674
00:53:03,890 --> 00:53:07,860
You had to stay. Someone needs
to take care of the boys, you know.

675
00:53:14,200 --> 00:53:15,570
Sergeant Park Beom-gu.

676
00:53:18,830 --> 00:53:19,830
You know…

677
00:53:22,750 --> 00:53:24,460
You've taught me so very much.

678
00:53:27,920 --> 00:53:29,040
I appreciate it.

679
00:53:42,220 --> 00:53:44,770
The tofu was my idea.

680
00:53:45,270 --> 00:53:46,850
Of course it was.

681
00:53:58,410 --> 00:54:02,410
TO INCHEON

682
00:54:02,490 --> 00:54:07,920
TO YONGDAM-RI

683
00:54:11,750 --> 00:54:14,970
Hmm. To think it's our last time
in a terminal together.

684
00:54:18,050 --> 00:54:19,180
Does it make you sad?

685
00:54:19,680 --> 00:54:21,810
I don't feel sad one bit, okay?

686
00:54:22,760 --> 00:54:24,100
I couldn't feel better.

687
00:54:27,600 --> 00:54:30,150
-I'll always keep in touch.
-Don't bother.

688
00:54:32,110 --> 00:54:35,400
I have never seen a junior
contact their superior after a discharge.

689
00:54:36,030 --> 00:54:38,950
And I hate when people contact me
on a personal basis.

690
00:54:39,660 --> 00:54:40,700
Let's stop here.

691
00:54:46,910 --> 00:54:48,250
Hmm…

692
00:54:48,830 --> 00:54:49,830
Jun-ho.

693
00:54:57,510 --> 00:54:59,260
I guess we're all done now, right?

694
00:55:03,010 --> 00:55:05,930
What are you talking about?
I don't think I've even gotten started.

695
00:55:12,900 --> 00:55:14,980
-The 3:30 p.m. bus…
-Oh, my bus is here.

696
00:55:15,480 --> 00:55:17,070
…will soon be departing.

697
00:55:17,150 --> 00:55:21,030
All passengers, please come
to the boarding zone to board the bus.

698
00:55:22,620 --> 00:55:23,530
I repeat.

699
00:55:24,580 --> 00:55:28,620
The 3:30 p.m. bus to Incheon
will soon be departing.

700
00:55:29,120 --> 00:55:32,130
All passengers, please come
to the boarding zone to board…

701
00:55:32,210 --> 00:55:35,300
It'll take a long time
to get there so rest up.

702
00:55:35,840 --> 00:55:38,670
Sleep is vital for a D.P., you know?

703
00:55:42,930 --> 00:55:43,890
Brother…

704
00:55:52,100 --> 00:55:53,150
Goodbye.

705
00:56:01,740 --> 00:56:02,740
See you.

706
00:56:46,740 --> 00:56:48,990
Seriously,
is he gonna come or what?

707
00:56:49,490 --> 00:56:51,580
-Why aren't they coming?
-Don't be mad.

708
00:56:51,660 --> 00:56:53,330
-Hey, guys.
-Hey. Sorry, I'm really late.

709
00:56:53,420 --> 00:56:55,290
-It wasn't me.
-So annoying.

710
00:56:55,380 --> 00:56:57,590
It's him. He went to the bathroom.

711
00:56:57,670 --> 00:56:59,460
You guys
wanna get coffee after this?

712
00:56:59,550 --> 00:57:00,550
