-Yeah.

713
00:57:07,470 --> 00:57:08,390
Let's go.

714
00:57:09,180 --> 00:57:10,060
Come on.

715
00:57:16,400 --> 00:57:17,900
Hey, what are you doing?

716
00:57:58,770 --> 00:58:00,940
I've met so many people
in the military.

717
00:58:02,400 --> 00:58:04,400
And I've said goodbyes to many, too.

718
00:58:05,780 --> 00:58:07,280
Will they remember me?

719
00:58:09,200 --> 00:58:11,200
Will I be able to remember them?

